    &kp ESC                   &kp EXCL                 &kp AT                    &kp HASH                &kp DLLR                      &kp PRCNT                &kp CARET                &kp AMPS                 &kp KP_ASTERISK          &kp LPAR                &kp RPAR                 &kp BSPC
